## ğŸ”§ Development

```bash
# Setup
git clone https://github.com/JFK/kagura-ai.git
cd kagura-ai
uv sync --all-extras

# Test
pytest -n auto

# Type check
pyright src/kagura/

# Lint
ruff check src/
```

See [CONTRIBUTING.md](./CONTRIBUTING.md) for details.

